      • add

        public double add(ODPair od,
                  double volume)
        Adds the given volume to the demand corresponding to the given o-d pair. You can use negative numbers to subtract. If the given volume is zero the call has no effect whatsoever other than returning the previous demand volume, if one exists.
        Parameters:
        od - Origin-Destination pair
        volume - the traffic volume to add (use negative numbers to subtract)
        Returns:
        the new total volume associated with the given od pair
